{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"大明山下阳春早","authors":["包玉堂"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":12,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大明山下阳春早〔仫佬族〕　包玉堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年前，华国锋同志曾到广西大明山下武鸣县壮族山乡视察，把毛主席为首的党中央对壮族人民的关怀，带给万户千家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报春鸟来叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红棉已含苞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大明山下阳春早呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水牛撞门马闹槽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处传捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔豪情关不住呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮乡腊月涨春潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘五年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜鹊唱树梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华国锋同志视察到壮乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问寒问暖话滔滔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸我壮乡美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山好水好人更好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教导我们坚持大寨路呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里莫动摇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年到如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五次阳春闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击退多少妖风与恶浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮山壮水更娇娆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水任我调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山任我雕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮乡要织新壮锦呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四化”新图任我描！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"华国锋","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}